00:14:41.050 --> 00:14:45.320 align:middle line:84%
What are some of these fears
that we may need to overcome?

00:14:45.320 --> 00:14:48.250 align:middle line:84%
Well, one common fear that
people have with astral travel

00:14:48.250 --> 00:14:51.688 align:middle line:84%
