of the silver cord.

00:14:51.688 --> 00:14:53.230 align:middle line:84%
There's a lot of
literature out there

00:14:53.230 --> 00:14:55.440 align:middle line:84%
that says that when
we astral travel,

00:14:55.440 --> 00:14:59.170 align:middle line:84%
there is a silver cord that
connects us to our body.

00:14:59.170 --> 00:15:02.860 align:middle line:84%
