silver cord was ever severed,

00:15:02.860 --> 00:15:05.410 align:middle line:84%
we could lose our
way, and if we're

00:15:05.410 --> 00:15:09.070 align:middle line:84%
unable to get our way back
to our body, we might die.

00:15:09.070 --> 00:15:10.000 align:middle line:90%
But not to worry.

00:15:10.000 --> 00:15:11.380 align:middle line:90%
This is a myth.

00:15:11.380 --> 00:15:13.780 align:middle line:84%
The fear has been
used to scare people

00:15:13.780 --> 00:15:16.270 align:middle line:84%
from ever trying the art
of astral travel, which

00:15:16.270 --> 00:15:18.630 align:middle line:90%
is a huge disservice.

00:15:18.630 --> 00:15:21.280 align:middle line:84%
Astral travel is such
an important tool

00:15:21.280 --> 00:15:24.430 align:middle line:84%
for us to experience and
identify our true self

00:15:24.430 --> 00:15:26.960 align:middle line:90%
beyond our physical body.

00:15:26.960 --> 00:15:28.580 align:middle line:90%
We are multidimensional.

00:15:28.580 --> 00:15:30.860 align:middle line:90%
We are eternal beings.

00:15:30.860 --> 00:15:35.650 align:middle line:84%
We have never been born, and
therefore we can never die.

00:15:35.650 --> 00:15:39.520 align:middle line:84%
To be fed this fear that
if we leave our body,

00:15:39.520 --> 00:15:41.290 align:middle line:90%
