00:15:41.290 --> 00:15:44.140 align:middle line:90%
That's incredibly disempowering.

00:15:44.140 --> 00:15:47.470 align:middle line:84%
It's reinforcing the
idea that we are our body

00:15:47.470 --> 00:15:50.830 align:middle line:90%
