we have some sense of control.

00:15:57.910 --> 00:16:00.910 align:middle line:84%
We never need to
be afraid of that.

00:16:00.910 --> 00:16:02.380 align:middle line:84%
The worst thing
that would happen

00:16:02.380 --> 00:16:05.320 align:middle line:84%
