take over and get us

00:16:13.220 --> 00:16:16.700 align:middle line:90%
back to where we need to be.

00:16:16.700 --> 00:16:21.020 align:middle line:84%
Another fear that may come
up is that of losing control.

00:16:21.020 --> 00:16:23.570 align:middle line:84%
When I first started to
consciously astral travel,

00:16:23.570 --> 00:16:25.910 align:middle line:90%
