And it was coming from some
place very deep within.

00:16:29.870 --> 00:16:31.610 align:middle line:84%
At that time, I
was honestly trying

00:16:31.610 --> 00:16:33.780 align:middle line:84%
to control all
aspects of my life.

00:16:33.780 --> 00:16:36.590 align:middle line:84%
