00:19:03.650 --> 00:19:05.570 align:middle line:90%
So what do we need to know?

00:19:05.570 --> 00:19:09.350 align:middle line:84%
Let's take a deeper look at some
of the dos and don'ts of astral

00:19:09.350 --> 00:19:11.090 align:middle line:90%
