life or in the afterlife,

00:19:46.430 --> 00:19:49.400 align:middle line:84%
those people who do
will have to face

00:19:49.400 --> 00:19:53.480 align:middle line:84%
the consequences of violating
another person's free will.

00:19:53.480 --> 00:19:56.240 align:middle line:84%
