00:24:00.040 --> 00:24:02.560 align:middle line:90%
How do we prepare ourselves?

00:24:02.560 --> 00:24:04.270 align:middle line:84%
Well, there are
three areas that we

00:24:04.270 --> 00:24:08.230 align:middle line:84%
need to prepare before we begin
our astral travel journey.

00:24:08.230 --> 00:24:13.390 align:middle line:84%
These are our environment,
our body, and our mind.

00:24:13.390 --> 00:24:17.860 align:middle line:84%
To begin with, our environment
should be clean and organized.

00:24:17.860 --> 00:24:21.070 align:middle line:84%
We want to avoid clutter
or too much chaos.

00:24:21.070 --> 00:24:24.340 align:middle line:84%
Those things affect
our state of mind.

00:24:24.340 --> 00:24:27.940 align:middle line:84%
The next area we need to
repair is our physical body.

00:24:27.940 --> 00:24:29.950 align:middle line:84%
Just like having a
clean space, it's

00:24:29.950 --> 00:24:33.400 align:middle line:84%
important that our physical
body is clean, too.

00:24:33.400 --> 00:24:36.070 align:middle line:84%
We can prepare with
a warm shower or bath

00:24:36.070 --> 00:24:37.870 align:middle line:90%
to help us relax.

00:24:37.870 --> 00:24:40.630 align:middle line:84%
And it's best to be relaxed
and also well-rested

00:24:40.630 --> 00:24:44.170 align:middle line:84%
