00:24:52.360 --> 00:24:55.000 align:middle line:84%
Also, avoid caffeine
or chocolate,

00:24:55.000 --> 00:24:57.710 align:middle line:84%
and don't use any
drugs, alcohol,

00:24:57.710 --> 00:25:01.150 align:middle line:84%
or mind-altering substances
before astral travel.

00:25:01.150 --> 00:25:07.510 align:middle line:84%
We need to be clear, focused,
and in control of our mind.

00:25:07.510 --> 00:25:12.490 align:middle line:84%
Preparing the mind is key
to successful astral travel.

00:25:12.490 --> 00:25:15.250 align:middle line:84%
We want the mind to
be calm and tranquil,

00:25:15.250 --> 00:25:18.480 align:middle line:84%
not focused on the
stress of life.

00:25:18.480 --> 00:25:21.120 align:middle line:84%
Also, when we consciously
astral travel,

00:25:21.120 --> 00:25:25.080 align:middle line:84%
