directing our journey,

00:25:25.080 --> 00:25:29.370 align:middle line:84%
so we have to have a clear
idea of where we're going.

00:25:29.370 --> 00:25:32.640 align:middle line:84%
It's up to us to pick the
exact location or dimension

00:25:32.640 --> 00:25:38.130 align:middle line:84%
that we're traveling to,
including how to get there.

00:25:38.130 --> 00:25:40.620 align:middle line:84%
One step that is
very important when

00:25:40.620 --> 00:25:42.570 align:middle line:84%
it comes to preparing
our environment

00:25:42.570 --> 00:25:45.420 align:middle line:90%
is to create sacred space.

00:25:45.420 --> 00:25:48.420 align:middle line:84%
This sacred space protects
us during the astral travel

00:25:48.420 --> 00:25:50.040 align:middle line:90%
experience.

00:25:50.040 --> 00:25:52.200 align:middle line:84%
I'm going to hand down
to you a tool called

00:25:52.200 --> 00:25:54.140 align:middle line:90%
the circle of protection.

00:25:54.140 --> 00:25:56.160 align:middle line:84%
And this is something
you can use to create

00:25:56.160 --> 00:25:59.290 align:middle line:90%
sacred space for your journey.

00:25:59.290 --> 00:26:02.520 align:middle line:84%
We start with our hands
in a triangle position,

00:26:02.520 --> 00:26:05.880 align:middle line:84%
with the thumbs and
index fingers touching.

00:26:05.880 --> 00:26:08.040 align:middle line:84%
We then turn it
over and point it

00:26:08.040 --> 00:26:11.970 align:middle line:84%
at the hara, just about
an inch below the navel.

00:26:11.970 --> 00:26:14.790 align:middle line:84%
With intention
and visualization,

00:26:14.790 --> 00:26:17.280 align:middle line:84%
we breathe with chi
while tracing out

00:26:17.280 --> 00:26:19.350 align:middle line:90%
a circle around the seat.

00:26:19.350 --> 00:26:22.170 align:middle line:90%


00:26:22.170 --> 00:26:24.960 align:middle line:84%
Be sure to touch the thumbs
and index fingers here again

00:26:24.960 --> 00:26:27.750 align:middle line:84%
at the far end of the
circle to close it.

00:26:27.750 --> 00:26:31.500 align:middle line:84%
Then retrace the circle
and bring the fingers back

00:26:31.500 --> 00:26:34.170 align:middle line:90%
to touching again at the hara.

00:26:34.170 --> 00:26:38.220 align:middle line:84%
We repeat this movement two
