Next, let's work
with three exercises

00:26:50.940 --> 00:26:54.930 align:middle line:84%
that build our foundation
for safe astral travel.

00:26:54.930 --> 00:26:57.150 align:middle line:84%
These exercises
can be done daily

00:26:57.150 --> 00:27:00.870 align:middle line:84%
to start building those
energetic muscles.

00:27:00.870 --> 00:27:04.740 align:middle line:84%
When it comes to astral travel,
we need to stay focused.

00:27:04.740 --> 00:27:08.640 align:middle line:84%
This relies on our ability
to discipline our will

00:27:08.640 --> 00:27:13.590 align:middle line:84%
and keep our attention
focused on a singular point.

00:27:13.590 --> 00:27:15.480 align:middle line:84%
Our body position
for this technique

00:27:15.480 --> 00:27:20.070 align:middle line:84%
is best done sitting up with
the spine somewhat straight.

00:27:20.070 --> 00:27:22.170 align:middle line:84%
Before starting
these exercises, plan

00:27:22.170 --> 00:27:24.540 align:middle line:84%
for at least 15
minutes of meditation

00:27:24.540 --> 00:27:27.180 align:middle line:90%
to relax and calm your mind.

00:27:27.180 --> 00:27:30.150 align:middle line:84%
Begin transitioning into
that alpha brainwave state

00:27:30.150 --> 00:27:36.540 align:middle line:84%
of 8 to 15 Hertz, and breathing
in, just relaxing your body,

00:27:36.540 --> 00:27:41.430 align:middle line:84%
allowing your attention to
shift into the inner planes.

00:27:41.430 --> 00:27:45.000 align:middle line:84%
Connect to your divinity and
feel that positive energy

00:27:45.000 --> 00:27:47.160 align:middle line:90%
flowing through you.

00:27:47.160 --> 00:27:52.650 align:middle line:84%
After 15 minutes of meditation,
then move into these exercises.

00:27:52.650 --> 00:27:54.920 align:middle line:84%
Each exercise can
be done for one week

00:27:54.920 --> 00:27:57.620 align:middle line:90%
before moving on to the next.

00:27:57.620 --> 00:28:00.710 align:middle line:84%
So on week one, begin
working with the image

00:28:00.710 --> 00:28:03.230 align:middle line:90%
of a dot on a wall.

00:28:03.230 --> 00:28:05.930 align:middle line:84%
It can be a black
dot on a white wall,

00:28:05.930 --> 00:28:09.380 align:middle line:90%
or a white dot on a black wall.

00:28:09.380 --> 00:28:11.750 align:middle line:84%
If it helps you,
you can first do

00:28:11.750 --> 00:28:14.480 align:middle line:84%
it physically, with
construction paper

00:28:14.480 --> 00:28:19.770 align:middle line:84%
or using a black circle on a
blank piece of white paper.

00:28:19.770 --> 00:28:25.050 align:middle line:84%
Focus on the dot with your
eyes open for five minutes,

00:28:25.050 --> 00:28:28.260 align:middle line:84%
then close your eyes
for five minutes.

00:28:28.260 --> 00:28:31.620 align:middle line:84%
Set a timer, and when
you close your eyes,

00:28:31.620 --> 00:28:36.480 align:middle line:84%
recreate the dot on the
wall within your mind.

00:28:36.480 --> 00:28:39.490 align:middle line:90%
Hold the image.

00:28:39.490 --> 00:28:42.990 align:middle line:84%
Notice how much
your mind wanders.

00:28:42.990 --> 00:28:44.940 align:middle line:84%
When you catch your
mind wandering,

00:28:44.940 --> 00:28:48.890 align:middle line:84%
gently bring it back
to the dot on the wall,

00:28:48.890 --> 00:28:50.100 align:middle line:90%
and hold that focus.

00:28:50.100 --> 00:28:52.990 align:middle line:90%


00:28:52.990 --> 00:28:55.330 align:middle line:84%
Building focus is
an essential part

00:28:55.330 --> 00:28:58.810 align:middle line:84%
of being able to direct and
control our astral travel

00:28:58.810 --> 00:29:00.520 align:middle line:90%
experience.

00:29:00.520 --> 00:29:04.060 align:middle line:84%
Practice this four times a day
for five to 10 minutes each

00:29:04.060 --> 00:29:05.260 align:middle line:90%
time.

00:29:05.260 --> 00:29:08.510 align:middle line:84%
The more you do this dot
on the wall exercise,

00:29:08.510 --> 00:29:11.140 align:middle line:84%
the more you will find that
you can control your mind

00:29:11.140 --> 00:29:14.555 align:middle line:84%
and hold your focused attention
on that singular point.

00:29:14.555 --> 00:29:17.120 align:middle line:90%


00:29:17.120 --> 00:29:21.600 align:middle line:84%
On week two, we'll add
on to this exercise.

00:29:21.600 --> 00:29:24.680 align:middle line:84%
Once you've firmly established
the dot on the wall

00:29:24.680 --> 00:29:29.210 align:middle line:84%
within your mind, hold that
focus for five minutes.

00:29:29.210 --> 00:29:33.860 align:middle line:90%
Next, imagine the dot expanding.

00:29:33.860 --> 00:29:38.450 align:middle line:84%
Expand the dot until it
touches the edges of the wall.

00:29:38.450 --> 00:29:42.020 align:middle line:84%
As the dot expands,
this now represents

00:29:42.020 --> 00:29:45.950 align:middle line:84%
the veil between the
