this expanded dot and feel it.

00:29:50.660 --> 00:29:52.580 align:middle line:84%
You can even pass
your hand through it

00:29:52.580 --> 00:29:55.280 align:middle line:90%
and get a sense of its texture.

00:29:55.280 --> 00:29:57.710 align:middle line:84%
Don't move through
it entirely yet.

00:29:57.710 --> 00:30:00.110 align:middle line:84%
Just keep working
with controlling

00:30:00.110 --> 00:30:05.120 align:middle line:84%
the expansion of the dot and
get familiar with the veil.

00:30:05.120 --> 00:30:08.900 align:middle line:84%
Again, continue working with
this exercise four times a day

00:30:08.900 --> 00:30:11.390 align:middle line:90%
for about 10 minutes each time.

00:30:11.390 --> 00:30:15.830 align:middle line:84%
Then on week three, we're ready
to start astral traveling.

00:30:15.830 --> 00:30:18.380 align:middle line:84%
Prepare by having
your destination

00:30:18.380 --> 00:30:20.540 align:middle line:90%
in mind before you begin.

00:30:20.540 --> 00:30:22.130 align:middle line:90%
Get clear on it.

00:30:22.130 --> 00:30:25.620 align:middle line:84%
Plan it out and
then write it down.

00:30:25.620 --> 00:30:29.330 align:middle line:84%
It may be helpful to set a
timer for about 30 to 45 minutes

00:30:29.330 --> 00:30:32.220 align:middle line:84%
to control the length
of your journey.

00:30:32.220 --> 00:30:35.420 align:middle line:84%
Remember to prepare your
physical space, your body,

00:30:35.420 --> 00:30:39.550 align:middle line:90%
and your mind before you begin.

00:30:39.550 --> 00:30:44.530 align:middle line:84%
Once you're ready, start with
the dot on the wall as before,

00:30:44.530 --> 00:30:49.400 align:middle line:84%
